Package: SingleCellGeneExplore
Title: Comprehensive Tools for Single-Cell RNA-seq Analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Sri Harsha",
           family = "Meghadri",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "harshameghadri@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Author: Sri Harsha Meghadri [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Sri Harsha Meghadri <harshameghadri@gmail.com>
Description: A comprehensive collection of helper functions for single-cell RNA 
    sequencing analysis. This package provides tools for data processing, 
    differential expression analysis, pathway enrichment analysis, and advanced 
    visualization of single-cell sequencing data. Includes utilities for working 
    with Seurat objects, pseudobulk analysis, cell cycle analysis, and generating 
    publication-ready plots including volcano plots, heatmaps, and violin plots.
